              int buildPrice,
              java.lang.String color)
        Street constructor. Used to create a Street object.
        Parameters:
        fieldID - is the ID/position of the field.
        fieldName - Determines the name of the field
        fieldInfo - Describes the information about the field (delete?)
        price - Determines the acquisition price
        baseRent - Determines the rent
        houseRent_1 - Determines the rent when the field got a house
        houseRent_2 - Determines the rent when the field got two houses
        houseRent_3 - Determines the rent when the field got three houses
        houseRent_4 - Determines the rent when the field got four houses
        hotelRent - Determines the rent when the field got a hotel
        buildPrice - Determines the price of expanding the Street field with extra houses/ a hotel
        color - Determines the color of the field to categorize the streets
